# Ignore SQL files everywhere
*.sql
**/*.sql

# Ignore README files
README.md
**/README.md

# Ignore any migration files and directories
**/migrations/**
**/*migration*
migrations/
**/migrations/

# Ignore hidden files
.*
**/.*

# Ignore test files
*.test.ts
*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts

# Ignore documentation
*.md
**/*.md

# Explicitly ignore the migrations directory at root level
../migrations/
../migrations/**

